{"type": "article", "id": 3129, "title": "柠檬榨汁器", "description": "", "date": "2014-10-29T07:25:29Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 3, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605232721SBcObCJjs016I32M.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t牛排、沙拉、生鱼片……在享用许多美食时我们都需要添加一点柠檬汁，以更好地激发出食物的味道。但是，切柠檬、挤柠檬也太麻烦啦，不妨试试印度设计师 Viraj Joshi 带来的这款柠檬榨汁器 Citro 吧。这是一款侧向榨汁器，与其他的榨汁器不同，它会将整颗柠檬放入榨汁器当中，类似于钳子一般形状的榨汁器会将其从中间一劈两半，更加便于用户取用其中的柠檬汁。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232718adXKeEiDskrMpS27.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0421875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232719BPiv5R4MLpWguoKx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.2203125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232719v7IRwnLHaUydCJSx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.9046875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232720aMfokU3EdKGQYOWT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}